    <briefdescription>
<para>Unique type identifier for command types. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1core_1_1data_1_1CommandTypeId" kindref="compound">CommandTypeId</ref> assigns a unique, monotonically increasing integer ID to each command type at compile time. The ID is generated once per type via TypeIndexer and cached in a function-local static.</para>
<para>Suitable for use as an array index or hash key.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>TypeIndexer </para>
